data.description: Welcome to this custom built home with pride of ownership! Original owners who loved and cared for this property. This home is 2569 sqft and has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The layout of the home is open and offers a family room, formal living room, formal dining room, and an office. Each bedroom is spacious. The  floor plan is spilt which offers extra privacy for the primary bedroom. Enjoy the beautiful desert sunrises and sunsets from your  beautiful enclosed sun room. Read a book and catch up on the day in this relaxing space with views of the Hesperia golf course and our beautiful mountains. This property sits on just under an acre of land. With an extra deep 3 car garage and circular driveway you have plenty of space for your toys and vehicles. Make this home your own today, you're going to love it!
